            <title>[SOLR-8601] RollupStream loses the type for group by buckets</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8601</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The RollupStream converts all buckets values to Strings. For example when grouping by year, month, day the numeric bucket values are converted to Strings. This displays fine but causes sorting bugs when sorting on bucket values because numbers are sorted as Strings.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
